cause.description:
Culture Shock Oakland is a non profit organization which focuses on youth outreach. We bring the youth into a positive enviroment and give them something to do(dance) to keep them out of the streets.
1. Create a positive environment for the up coming youth
cause.mission: "We are a troupe of indivduals who through the power of music and dance cultivate dignity, self worth, and respect for all people."
cause.name: Culture Shock Oakland
